{"status":200,"code":1000,"message":null,"timestamp":"1762171066711","path":null,"data":{"id":1346,"title":"AIA:推出「友心意」醫療保障計劃2及停售安排","type":"PRODUCT_NEWS","time":1666670891303,"tags":["友邦保險"],"content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">致合作夥伴：</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong> 1）友邦</strong>誠意於<strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">2022年10月24日(以保單申請日起計)</span></strong>推出<strong><span style=\"color: #f80871;\">「友心意」醫療保障計劃2</span></strong>，提升計劃保障及增添增值服務，為客戶提供更全面的保障。</span></p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">全新VIP計劃:每病症限額高達HKD/MOP 1,000,000，並尊享額外保障</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #df138d; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>可享首個保單年度9折保費折扣</strong></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">為癌症及腎病的長期病況提供額外支援</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">增設住院/日間手術前門診諮詢及其他保障項目</span></li>\n<li>\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">所有計劃級別設有優質醫療網絡及環球緊急支援服務，計劃三/四設<span style=\"color: #000000;\">個人療程管理服務與復康管理</span>，計劃二至四本地免找數醫療服務伸展至適用於海外</span></div>\n</li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">增長遞交申請時段，放寬AIA團體醫療保險計劃成員家屬投保要求</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong> 2）<span style=\"color: #f80871;\">「友心意」醫療保障計劃</span></strong>已於<strong><span style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">2022年10月23日停止銷售</span></strong>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 詳情請參閱附件。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><!--EndFragment--></span></p>","attachments":[{"fileName":"Memo.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2022-10-25/efd5fb5fcfe04102a92a368a610a790f.pdf","uploadTime":1666663150025,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"「友心意」醫療保障計劃2.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2022-10-25/b3573eb815f944a39a2eb371b5be0989.pdf","uploadTime":1666663157304,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"StepUp Medical Protection Plan 2.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2022-10-25/6804576ba7774ba69f5d090b083881cd.pdf","uploadTime":1666663160970,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"產品投保申請書.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2022-10-25/f5d0427a60c645d7b701d59c9339a5a6.pdf","uploadTime":1666663164948,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null}],"companyCode":"AIA","companyName":"友邦保險","productCodes":["AIA:SUMPP2","AIA:FMIP"],"productNames":["友心意醫療保障計劃2","友心意醫療保障計劃"],"companyCodes":["AIA"],"companyNames":["友邦保險"],"startEffectiveDate":1666575672904,"endEffectiveDate":null,"effective":true}}